snippet.title: Castle Crumble Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Castle Crumble - a mobile game released into the Apple Arcade family with a blast, taking the platform by storm! 

Castle Keepers are waiting for you in their fortresses - can you crumble your way through?

Follow us on Twitter for more fun content and updates: https://twitter.com/orbital_knight

If you have any questions, don't hesitate to ask at support@orbitalknight.com 
We also look forward to your feedback about our game!
